  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7421323/" class="title-link">中国震撼世界</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7421323"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/31678134/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u31678134-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/31678134/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">King</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-03-22"
      class="main-meta">2015-03-22 16:24:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7421323_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  　　这是一本少见的由记者写成的关于中国革命的记录作品，作者水平可能有限，没法写出《第三帝国的兴亡》之类的著作，但他也没有如史沫特莱一样只接触中共的高层领导。而是深入到华北解放区，通过一双记者的眼睛去看，去报导了一些关于中国革命的内容。他算是深入普通民众，接...

